import React from 'react';
import { 
  Box, 
  Container, 
  Typography, 
  Grid, 
  Paper, 
  List, 
  ListItem, 
  ListItemIcon, 
  ListItemText,
  useTheme, 
  useMediaQuery,
  Button
} from '@mui/material';
import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';
import {
  Bookmark as BookmarkIcon,
  Devices as DevicesIcon,
  Speed as SpeedIcon,
  Search as SearchIcon,
  Book as BookIcon,
  Person as PersonIcon,
  CloudSync as CloudSyncIcon,
  FormatSize as FormatSizeIcon,
  DarkMode as DarkModeIcon,
  Notifications as NotificationsIcon
} from '@mui/icons-material';

const features = [
  {
    title: 'Extensive Library',
    description: 'Access thousands of books across all genres.',
    icon: <BookIcon fontSize="large" />,
    details: [
      'Wide range of genres and categories',
      'New releases and bestsellers',
      'Personalized recommendations',
      'Save books to your reading list'
    ]
  },
  {
    title: 'Seamless Reading',
    description: 'Enjoy a distraction-free reading experience.',
    icon: <BookmarkIcon fontSize="large" />,
    details: [
      'Customizable font sizes and styles',
      'Day and night reading modes',
      'Page turn animations',
      'Bookmark your favorite pages'
    ]
  },
  {
    title: 'Cross-Device Sync',
    description: 'Pick up where you left off on any device.',
    icon: <DevicesIcon fontSize="large" />,
    details: [
      'Sync across all your devices',
      'Automatic progress saving',
      'Offline reading available',
      'Cloud backup of your library'
    ]
  },
  {
    title: 'Smart Search',
    description: 'Find exactly what you\'re looking for.',
    icon: <SearchIcon fontSize="large" />,
    details: [
      'Search by title, author, or keyword',
      'Advanced filters and sorting',
      'Save your favorite searches',
      'Discover similar books'
    ]
  },
  {
    title: 'Reading Stats',
    description: 'Track your reading habits and progress.',
    icon: <SpeedIcon fontSize="large" />,
    details: [
      'Time spent reading',
      'Books completed',
      'Reading speed analysis',
      'Personal reading challenges'
    ]
  },
  {
    title: 'Personalized Profile',
    description: 'Make it truly yours.',
    icon: <PersonIcon fontSize="large" />,
    details: [
      'Custom reading preferences',
      'Reading goals and achievements',
      'Personal notes and highlights',
      'Follow your favorite authors'
    ]
  }
];

const FeaturesPage = () => {
  const theme = useTheme();
  const navigate = useNavigate();
  const isMobile = useMediaQuery(theme.breakpoints.down('sm'));

  return (
    <Box sx={{ py: 8 }}>
      {/* Hero Section */}
      <Box 
        sx={{
          bgcolor: 'primary.main',
          color: 'primary.contrastText',
          py: 12,
          mb: 8,
          textAlign: 'center'
        }}
      >
        <Container maxWidth="md">
          <Typography 
            variant={isMobile ? 'h3' : 'h2'} 
            component="h1"
            gutterBottom
            sx={{ fontWeight: 'bold' }}
          >
            Features
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ maxWidth: 800, mx: 'auto', opacity: 0.9 }}>
            Discover everything our e-reader platform has to offer
          </Typography>
        </Container>
      </Box>

      {/* Main Features */}
      <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ mb: 8 }}>
        <Grid container spacing={4}>
          {features.map((feature, index) => (
            <Grid item xs={12} md={6} lg={4} key={index}>
              <Paper 
                elevation={3} 
                sx={{ 
                  height: '100%',
                  p: 4,
                  display: 'flex',
                  flexDirection: 'column',
                  transition: 'transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s',
                  '&:hover': {
                    transform: 'translateY(-8px)',
                    boxShadow: theme.shadows[8]
                  }
                }}
              >
                <Box 
                  sx={{
                    width: 64,
                    height: 64,
                    borderRadius: '50%',
                    bgcolor: 'primary.main',
                    display: 'flex',
                    alignItems: 'center',
                    justifyContent: 'center',
                    color: 'primary.contrastText',
                    mb: 3,
                    alignSelf: 'center'
                  }}
                >
                  {React.cloneElement(feature.icon, { fontSize: 'large' })}
                </Box>
                <Typography variant="h5" component="h3" gutterBottom align="center">
                  {feature.title}
                </Typography>
                <Typography 
                  color="text.secondary" 
                  align="center"
                  sx={{ mb: 3 }}
                >
                  {feature.description}
                </Typography>
                <List dense>
                  {feature.details.map((detail, i) => (
                    <ListItem key={i} disableGutters>
                      <ListItemIcon sx={{ minWidth: 36 }}>
                        <Box 
                          sx={{ 
                            width: 6, 
                            height: 6, 
                            borderRadius: '50%', 
                            bgcolor: 'primary.main',
                            opacity: 0.7
                          }} 
                        />
                      </ListItemIcon>
                      <ListItemText primary={detail} />
                    </ListItem>
                  ))}
                </List>
              </Paper>
            </Grid>
          ))}
        </Grid>
      </Container>

      {/* Additional Features Section */}
      <Box sx={{ bgcolor: 'background.paper', py: 8 }}>
        <Container maxWidth="lg">
          <Typography 
            variant="h4" 
            component="h2" 
            align="center" 
            gutterBottom
            sx={{ mb: 6 }}
          >
            More Great Features
          </Typography>
          
          <Grid container spacing={6} alignItems="center">
            <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
              <Box sx={{ maxWidth: 600, mx: 'auto' }}>
                <Typography variant="h5" component="h3" gutterBottom>
                  Customizable Reading Experience
                </Typography>
                <Typography color="text.secondary" paragraph>
                  Tailor your reading experience to your preferences with our extensive customization options.
                </Typography>
                <List>
                  {[
                    { icon: <FormatSizeIcon color="primary" />, text: 'Adjustable font size and style' },
                    { icon: <DarkModeIcon color="primary" />, text: 'Dark mode and theme options' },
                    { icon: <CloudSyncIcon color="primary" />, text: 'Automatic cloud sync' },
                    { icon: <NotificationsIcon color="primary" />, text: 'Reading reminders and notifications' }
                  ].map((item, index) => (
                    <ListItem key={index} disableGutters>
                      <ListItemIcon sx={{ minWidth: 40 }}>
                        {item.icon}
                      </ListItemIcon>
                      <ListItemText primary={item.text} />
                    </ListItem>
                  ))}
                </List>
              </Box>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
              <Box 
                sx={{
                  bgcolor: 'action.hover',
                  borderRadius: 2,
                  p: 4,
                  height: '100%',
                  display: 'flex',
                  flexDirection: 'column',
                  justifyContent: 'center'
                }}
              >
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                  Ready to experience all these features?
                </Typography>
                <Typography color="text.secondary" sx={{ mb: 3 }}>
                  Join thousands of readers who have already enhanced their reading experience with our platform.
                </Typography>
                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', gap: 2, flexWrap: 'wrap' }}>
                  <Button 
                    variant="contained" 
                    color="primary" 
                    size="large"
                    onClick={() => navigate('/register')}
                  >
                    Sign Up Free
                  </Button>
                  <Button 
                    variant="outlined" 
                    color="primary" 
                    size="large"
                    onClick={() => navigate('/about')}
                  >
                    Learn More About Us
                  </Button>
                </Box>
              </Box>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Container>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default FeaturesPage;
